# Requirements Specification

## Functional Requirements
FR01: The system shall allow users to create an account and log in  
FR02: The system shall display a list of restaurants  
FR03: The system shall allow users to view menus  
FR04: The system shall allow users to add items to cart  
FR05: The system shall allow users to place orders  
FR06: The system shall allow users to track order status  
FR07: The system shall allow admin to manage restaurant listings  

## Non-Functional Requirements
NFR01: The system shall load pages within 3 seconds  
NFR02: The system shall be available 24/7  
NFR03: The system shall support at least 200 concurrent users  
NFR04: The system shall ensure secure payment processing  
NFR05: The system interface shall be mobile-friendly  
